  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A brutal murder inside a collapsed broadcast studio.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Uncover the hidden truth through <strong>Communication x Survival x Adventure</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1025960/extras/f114058466268685a479535bbb3cb880.avif?t=1747276302\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1025960/extras_big/f114058466268685a479535bbb3cb880.avif?t=1747276302 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Buried Stars</i> is a mystery adventure game from Studio LARGO—the creators of the beloved Korean titles <i>Panic Room</i> and <i>City of Mist</i>—in collaboration with LINE Games.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Murder at a Survival Audition Gone Wrong</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1025960/extras/93f2d6f95d7717978d069ca5f5b30500.poster.avif?t=1747276302\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1025960/extras/93f2d6f95d7717978d069ca5f5b30500.webm?t=1747276302\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1025960/extras/93f2d6f95d7717978d069ca5f5b30500.mp4?t=1747276302\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >During a live broadcast of a survival audition show, the studio building suddenly collapses.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Trapped beneath the rubble, the remaining contestants and crew face something even more terrifying: a murder among them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Who is the culprit? Why did this happen? And how?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Striking Visual Presentation with 3D x 2D Harmony</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dynamic 2D character illustrations are blended into detailed 3D environments</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >to create an atmospheric and cinematic visual experience.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Immersive Gameplay through Social Media Mechanics</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1025960/extras/186ed3f84d6e23a91deef0b32806172e.avif?t=1747276302\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1025960/extras_big/186ed3f84d6e23a91deef0b32806172e.avif?t=1747276302 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Keep track of real-time public reactions via the in-game “Social Media” and “Timeline.”</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >These systems not only deepen the immersion but also provide crucial hints to help uncover the truth.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Branching Scenarios and Multiple Endings</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1025960/extras/38b459a5c8551f66822f300ce186cf5d.avif?t=1747276302\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1025960/extras_big/38b459a5c8551f66822f300ce186cf5d.avif?t=1747276302 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your dialogue choices and actions shape the story.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With multiple routes, endings, and hidden stories, each playthrough reveals new truths—and new fates for the survivors.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Powerful Soundtrack and Performances</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1025960/extras/dffc14a8c4ffde00de903c1d4d87cc05.poster.avif?t=1747276302\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1025960/extras/dffc14a8c4ffde00de903c1d4d87cc05.webm?t=1747276302\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1025960/extras/dffc14a8c4ffde00de903c1d4d87cc05.mp4?t=1747276302\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into the emotional intensity of the story with an original soundtrack, environmental sound design, and the gripping main theme, “Be Honest.”</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Stellar Voice Acting in Korean and Japanese</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1025960/extras/bda8e2667f7ed4ba0752855e32777530.poster.avif?t=1747276302\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1025960/extras/bda8e2667f7ed4ba0752855e32777530.webm?t=1747276302\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1025960/extras/bda8e2667f7ed4ba0752855e32777530.mp4?t=1747276302\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Featuring passionate performances by seasoned voice talent from both Korea and Japan:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Korean Cast</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Park Sungtae, Ryu Seunggon, Nam Dohyoung, Kim Yeonwoo, Kim Haru, Lee Kyoungtae, Lim Yoonsun, and more</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Japanese Cast</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Tetsuya Kakihara, Takuya Eguchi, Hiro Shimono, Yoko Hikasa, Rina Sato, Soichiro Hoshi, Eri Kitamura, and more</i></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A brutal murder inside a collapsed broadcast studio.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Uncover the hidden truth through <strong>Communication x Survival x Adventure</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1025960/extras/f114058466268685a479535bbb3cb880.avif?t=1747276302\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1025960/extras_big/f114058466268685a479535bbb3cb880.avif?t=1747276302 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Buried Stars</i> is a mystery adventure game from Studio LARGO—the creators of the beloved Korean titles <i>Panic Room</i> and <i>City of Mist</i>—in collaboration with LINE Games.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Murder at a Survival Audition Gone Wrong</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1025960/extras/93f2d6f95d7717978d069ca5f5b30500.poster.avif?t=1747276302\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1025960/extras/93f2d6f95d7717978d069ca5f5b30500.webm?t=1747276302\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1025960/extras/93f2d6f95d7717978d069ca5f5b30500.mp4?t=1747276302\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >During a live broadcast of a survival audition show, the studio building suddenly collapses.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Trapped beneath the rubble, the remaining contestants and crew face something even more terrifying: a murder among them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Who is the culprit? Why did this happen? And how?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Striking Visual Presentation with 3D x 2D Harmony</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dynamic 2D character illustrations are blended into detailed 3D environments</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >to create an atmospheric and cinematic visual experience.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Immersive Gameplay through Social Media Mechanics</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1025960/extras/186ed3f84d6e23a91deef0b32806172e.avif?t=1747276302\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1025960/extras_big/186ed3f84d6e23a91deef0b32806172e.avif?t=1747276302 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Keep track of real-time public reactions via the in-game “Social Media” and “Timeline.”</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >These systems not only deepen the immersion but also provide crucial hints to help uncover the truth.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Branching Scenarios and Multiple Endings</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1025960/extras/38b459a5c8551f66822f300ce186cf5d.avif?t=1747276302\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1025960/extras_big/38b459a5c8551f66822f300ce186cf5d.avif?t=1747276302 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your dialogue choices and actions shape the story.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With multiple routes, endings, and hidden stories, each playthrough reveals new truths—and new fates for the survivors.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Powerful Soundtrack and Performances</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1025960/extras/dffc14a8c4ffde00de903c1d4d87cc05.poster.avif?t